Core users and “groups”
	•	Customers (B2B buyers, retailers, clinics, plants)
	•	Distributors / wholesalers
	•	Manufacturers / suppliers
	•	3PL / warehouse ops
	•	Carriers / forwarders
	•	Internal (sales ops, customer success, supply planning, finance, QA)

